description: Introducing Kaos Silicone Ear Tunnels for women and men - the perfect ear accessories to showcase your unique sense of style! Crafted with expert precision, our ear tunnels are made from high-quality silicone that's both subtle and sophisticated.

Available in sizes ranging from 10g–1” (~2.5mm–25mm), our ear tunnels and plugs are designed to fit everyone comfortably. With a wearable area of 3/8” (~10mm), you can wear them all day long without experiencing any discomfort. Ideal earring plugs for men and women.

What sets our plugs and tunnels for ears apart is the subtle flares and a smooth finish that feels amazing to the touch. They are designed to create perfectly stretched piercings. Made to perfection, our products are sure to impress even the most discerning fashionistas.
So why settle for anything less than the best? Get your hands on Kaos Softwear Silicone Hider Plug Earrings today and experience the ultimate in comfort, style, and quality.
